definitions.definition: Corrupted or made impure by being mixed with something else; adulterated .
Tending to commit adultery ; relating to or being the product of adultery; adulterous .

main_definition: Corrupted or made impure by being mixed with something else; adulterated . [common in the 16th and 17th c.]
secondary_definitions: Tending to commit adultery ; relating to or being the product of adultery; adulterous . [common in the 16th and 17th c.]
